			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">Light at the End of the Tunnel</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">Millions of killer culverts lurk beneath North American roadways, strangling populations of migratory fish. Now with a nationwide project, the United States is trying to fix them.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/ben-goldfarb/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Ben Goldfarb</a>								<br/>
							Illustrations by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/maggie-chiang/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Maggie Chiang</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
